SPOR - Store Permissions and Ownership Recursively
==================================================
This project was started intending to provide a simple and safe method
to save and restore particular metadata information of a given directory.
Its primary goal is store this information in order to import (mostly) 
configuration directories in versioning repositories.

It is a very simple tool that walk down recursively throughout a given 
directory storing metadata related to file/directory modes and ownership
inside a regular text file, for future retrievals.

It is free software, covered by GNU General Public License,
and you are welcome to change it and/or distribute copies of it.
There is absolute no warranty for spor.
